high_descs: pick up the rag from the counter
go the sink on the right
wash the rag in the sink and remove
walk to the center of the room and face the toilet
put the washcloth in the cabinet below the sink
anns.task_desc: rinse the rag in the sink and put it in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the rag that is on the sink counter
Turn around, take a step forwards, and turn around again.
place the rag in the sink and turn the faucet on and off to wet the rag
Turn around, take a step forwards, and turn around again.
Place the wet rag in the cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a wet rag in the cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the blue cloth rag on the counter.
Pick up the cloth rag from the counter.
Move left slightly to the front of the sink on the right.
Put the cloth rag in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Move back slightly from the counter top.
Put the cloth rag in the bottom left cabinet below the sink, then close the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned cloth rag in a cabinet.
